title: $:/plugins/crosseye/json-convert/usage/tokens/piping
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

Add `|name` to send the resolved value through a registered transform
function.  The transform's output (still automatically string-coerced)
becomes the token's contribution.

```
"text": "{{message|html-to-wikitext}}"
"tags": "{{category|split-commas}}"
```
